cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL

The paper deals with 3D object detection in autonomous vehicles, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The use of ad-hoc regression branches and the elimination of a post-processing stage suggest that machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) are also relevant sub-categories. Finally, the paper involves the processing of LiDAR data, which could potentially fall under computational linguistics (cs.CL) due to the use of point clouds and spatial data.
